snippet.title: Feisty Fauna gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Feisty Fauna is a casual roguelite where you're a cute animal trying to survive by being feisty. Whether it's by traps, attacks, or minions, you will not succumb to being hunted like regular fauna! Instead, you will hunt other cute animals in this eat-or-be-eaten animal world.
Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/feistyfaunatrailer
